No.

106
00:04:45,977 --> 00:04:47,438
And, uh, later today,

107
00:04:47,538 --> 00:04:48,901
I need you to meet a team...

108
00:04:48,985 --> 00:04:50,610
...from county
at the loading dock.

109
00:04:50,742 --> 00:04:52,088
We're giving them PPE.

110
00:04:53,266 --> 00:04:56,063
