234
00:09:48,789 --> 00:09:50,544
I'm gonna lighten
her sedation...

235
00:09:51,784 --> 00:09:54,311
...and then gradually
turn down all of her settings.

236
00:09:54,395 --> 00:09:57,122
And if she tolerates it,
then we'll move forward

237
00:09:57,207 --> 00:09:58,786
with spontaneous
breathing trials.

238
00:09:58,871 --> 00:10:00,631
Dr. Altman, I'm more
than able to handle this

239
00:10:00,715 --> 00:10:01,884
with the
respiratory therapist.

240
00:10:01,968 --> 00:10:03,277
Maybe you should
get some rest.

241
00:10:03,361 --> 00:10:05,192
I know how closely
you worked with Dr. DeLuca.

242
00:10:05,276 --> 00:10:08,192
Which has nothing to do with
getting Meredith off the vent.

243
00:10:16,666 --> 00:10:18,146
Come on, Grey.

244
00:10:20,378 --> 00:10:22,411
Come on, Grey,
you can do this.

245
00:10:24,295 --> 00:10:26,419
You look just like Ellis
just now,

246
00:10:26,504 --> 00:10:27,686
the way you're looking
at your feet.

247
