653
00:30:02,159 --> 00:30:04,120
What did you do
to make her smile?

654
00:30:04,204 --> 00:30:05,462
You shoulda seen it...

655
00:30:05,547 --> 00:30:06,731
she smiles and she smiles,

656
00:30:06,815 --> 00:30:09,168
and it gets bigger
and bigger until...

657
00:30:09,252 --> 00:30:11,519
Boom!
