658
00:30:11,603 --> 00:30:14,043
What did you do
to make her laugh?

659
00:30:14,127 --> 00:30:16,045
Then her brother gets annoyed
because she's laughing so hard

660
00:30:16,129 --> 00:30:17,176
right in his ear.

661
00:30:17,260 --> 00:30:18,221
That's Bailey.

662
00:30:18,305 --> 00:30:19,614
And then the oldest one
comes in,

663
00:30:19,698 --> 00:30:22,181
