681
00:31:08,619 --> 00:31:11,639
I don't know that I can.

682
00:31:12,382 --> 00:31:15,553
It's... so warm here.

683
00:31:15,661 --> 00:31:17,927
The water is so cool.

684
00:31:18,210 --> 00:31:19,978
I feel so relaxed.

685
00:31:20,062 --> 00:31:21,719
And there's no pain.

686
00:31:21,803 --> 00:31:23,672
